# This service uses explicit environment files by execution context.
#
# Host-shell commands:
# - copy values from `.env.host` when running the service, tests, or
#   migrations from your machine
#
# Docker runtime:
# - copy values from `.env.docker` when running the service inside Docker
#   Compose
#
# Security-related runtime values currently live in `.env.host` and `.env.docker`:
# - `ENABLE_API_DOCS`
# - `RATE_LIMIT_TTL_MS`
# - `RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS`
#
# Do not treat this file as the source of runtime values.
